name: Tamara Parsons-Baker Solo EP: Lover
description:
Tamara releases her long-awaited solo EP 'Lover' on Big Red Sky Records. This EP includes the following 5 tracks, cover art by Toni Le Busque and a free badge:

1. Hang My Picture
2 Crying Wolf
3. I Stuck It Out
4. Get Him Out
5. Lover

name: Badges
description:
Badges and keyrings designed by the wonderful Toni Le Busque using lyrics from Tamara's songs. Order yours now to receive your badge and a personalised message from the band. 
All prices include postage and packaging.

Design your own unique badge:
If there are some lyrics you would like to see made into a badge or keyring then please contact us and we will get it made especially for you. 

If you would like a particular badge design please email us via the contact box and request your badge.
